    &ref.title.note;


You need an installed version of this software to use this
    task.

&ref.title.supportedNestedTags;
<fileset> This nested tag is required when the file attribute is not set.
<formatter> The results of the analysis can be printed in different formats.
Output will always be sent to STDOUT, unless you set the usefile attribute to true and set an filename in the outfile attribute.
Attributes for <formatter>
&taskAttributes.table.titlesLine.all;
type
String
The output format. Accepts the the same values as the format attribute (xml, html, text).
&attributes.defaultValue.NA;
&attributes.required.yes;
usefile
Boolean
Boolean that determines whether output should be sent to a file.
true
&attributes.required.no;
outfile
String
Path to write output file to.
&attributes.defaultValue.NA;
&attributes.required.yes;
